The Chinese modernization encompasses a huge population of common prosperity for all. The urban-rural income gap narrowing and talent introduction have accelerated industrial upgrades and rural revitalization, which strongly supports China's modernization. The development of China's countryside has taken on a new look in recent years and check out the latest episode of "Thought Bubble" to learn more! (To submit cartoons and share story ideas or feedback on our cartoon page, please contact us at cartoon_opinions@cgtn.com)